'''阿伯加文尼'''（{{lang-en|Abergavenny}}，{{lang-cy|Y Fenni}}）是[[英國|英國]][[威爾斯|威爾斯]]的一座城鎮，位於威爾斯東南部，其歷史可以追溯自[[羅馬帝國|羅馬帝國]]時期。因其地理位置，阿伯加文尼有「通往威爾斯的玄關」之稱<ref name="BBC">{{cite web | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/southeast/sites/abergavenny/pages/article_pip.shtml | title=The Gateway to Wales | author=BBC | accessdate=8 February 2011 | archive-date=2006-01-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060111111903/http://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/southeast/sites/abergavenny/pages/article_pip.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Frommers">{{cite web | url=http://www.frommers.com/destinations/abergavenny/2501010001.html | title=Introduction to Abergavenny | author=Frommers | accessdate=8 February 2011 | archive-date=2012-10-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016131958/http://www.frommers.com/destinations/abergavenny/2501010001.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
